headline: Will JPMorgan-Coinbase Tie-Up Bring Crypto Closer to Mainstream?
summary: JPM partners with COIN to enable direct crypto access, stablecoin rewards and tokenized banking. This marks a major step toward mainstream adoption of crypto.
